      "title": "Curfew for Colombo district",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Acting President Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe has arranged to impose curfew in the Colombo administrative district. Accordingly, curfew has been imposed from 12.00 noon today to 5.00 tomorrow morning."
